data.title: New Sky Max comedy series 'Funny Woman', starring Tom Bateman, Doon Mackichan & Olivia Williams.
data.meta_description: The life and journey of Barbara Parker, London's force behind 1960's cultural explosion. Watch on Sky Max.
data.text:
Watch Geraldine James, Rhashan Stone and Olivia Williams in episode 2 of 'Unprecedented'!

Series written and filmed in lockdown that responds to the radical way we have seen our world change during the coronavirus pandemic.

Join Gemma Whelan, Olivia Williams and Jemima Rooper in 15 Heroines.

15 leading British playwrights draw inspiration from Ovid to dramatise the lives of 15 Heroines. Delivered by an outstanding cast in three parts - The War, The Desert and The Labyrinth - 15 Heroines is a landmark theatrical brought to you from the Jermyn Street Theatre. The show will stream from 9th-14th November. Tickets still available.
